data.title: Roundel 1961-09 Vol 13 No 7
data.meta_description: Roundel 1961-09 Vol 13 No 7 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is a magazine from September 1961 about the Royal Canadian Air Force (RCAF). It discusses RCAF activities in the Congo over the past year, including air transport of troops and equipment as well as ground work. It previews upcoming articles about the history of RCAF Station Rockcliffe, an escape and evasion story from World War 2, and the new CF-101B aircraft being introduced to the RCAF. It also discusses initial experiences flying the CF-101B and CF-104 Starfighter interceptors.
